{
  "id": "6a2a7f00980502c1e05c17be",
  "title": "他者の靴は履いてはいけない",
  "created": 1781169940,
  "updated": 1781227340,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a2a7f00980502c1e05c17be",
      "text": "他者の靴は履いてはいけない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1781169940,
      "updated": 1781169940
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2a7f130000000000d37ff4",
      "text": "[水虫]（[足白癬]）が感染るから",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1781169940,
      "updated": 1781175264
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2a82db0000000000bd7090",
      "text": " 足湯もかなり[水虫]の原因となるらしい[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1781170907,
      "updated": 1781170925
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2a7f150000000000d37ff6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1781169941,
      "updated": 1781169941
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2a7f150000000000d37ff7",
      "text": "なので、「[他者の考え方や気持ちと同じ靴を履]」いう喩えが、とても気持ち悪かった [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1781169942,
      "updated": 1781189421
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2a7f140000000000d37ff5",
      "text": "「他者の靴を履く」というのはイギリスのことわざだったんだね",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1781169940,
      "updated": 1781170105
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2a89540000000000445126",
      "text": " わろた[はるひ.icon][kana.icon]",
      "userId": "5e9487d750011b001eb536eb",
      "created": 1781172565,
      "updated": 1781226018
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2a92a800000000000724ee",
      "text": " なるほど[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781174953,
      "updated": 1781174957
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2acb5a000000000047f6d7",
      "text": " +1[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1781189467,
      "updated": 1781189467
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2a7f8b0000000000d37ff8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1781170059,
      "updated": 1781170059
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2a838e0000000000951b59",
      "text": "自分の靴なら履いてもいいのかな[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1781171069,
      "updated": 1781171081
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2a83990000000000951b5b",
      "text": " 履いてはいけないときもありそう。汚れがひどいときとか",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1781171081,
      "updated": 1781171099
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2a85550000000000d0534d",
      "text": " 濡れた汚い靴とかも水虫なりそう[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1781171542,
      "updated": 1781171565
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2a838f0000000000951b5a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1781171070,
      "updated": 1781171070
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2a86fc0000000000ec1b31",
      "text": "格言的な話かと思ったら思いっきり物理だった[taktamur.icon][sta.icon][Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1781171964,
      "updated": 1781227340
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2a87010000000000ec1b32",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1781171969,
      "updated": 1781171969
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2a8bfd000000000091ff2d",
      "text": "[普段履いてる靴は一足][sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
